data.description: Open House cancelled Welcome to your dream home! Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, this exquisite 4-bedroom, single-family home offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and classic charm. With 2 full bathrooms and 2 half baths, this residence is designed to cater to the needs of your family seamlessly. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open and inviting floor plan, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The heart of the home is undoubtedly the fully renovated kitchen. Equipped with brand new appliances and adorned with contemporary finishes, this kitchen is as stylish as it is functional. Imagine preparing meals and creating memories in this gourmet space that seamlessly flows into the dining area, perfect for entertaining guests.  The home boasts not one, but three fully renovated bathrooms. The living room features a cozy fireplace, providing a focal point for relaxation and gatherings during colder evenings. The new roof adds not only to the aesthetic appeal but also ensures peace of mind with its durability and longevity. Beyond the walls of this elegant abode, discover the beauty of nature surrounding the community with walking trails. Conveniently located for an effortless commute, this property is not just a home; it's a lifestyle. Embrace the convenience of being close to key amenities, schools, and major transportation routes. This is not just a house; it's a haven where every detail has been carefully curated to create a perfect sanctuary for you and your loved ones. Welcome home to the life you've always dreamed of.
